of his/her accounts banned.<br><br>- The EverQuest Customer Service Team<br><br>Nice to know huh?<br><br><br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#564E39><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/umanaspineblade.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Manas Pineblade</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Protector of Lore</span><br>  Posts: 133<br> <font color=#F4CC10>(6/11/01 6:44:07 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fthecrossroadstavern8833frm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=252.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://209.208.244.106/comp403/jahearn/manas.jpg height = 153 width = 123></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Changes to Verant Policy</span><hr size=1> Verant: &quot;Bend over just a bit more...there!&quot;<br><br>Players: *cry* <p><TABLE BORDER="1" ALIGN="CENTER" BORDERCOLOR="#009900"bgcolor="#ffffff"><TR><TD align=center valign=middle BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF"><FONT FACE="Old English Text MT" COLOR="#009900" SIZE="6">Manas Pineblade</FONT></TD><TR><TD><A HREF="http://www.cofguild.org"><img border="0" src="http://www.cofguild.org/eq/logo3a.jpg" width="300" height="58"></a></TD><TR><TD ALIGN=RIGHT BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" VALIGN="CENTER"><FONT FACE="Old English Text MT" COLOR="#009900" SIZE="3">Officer and Founding Member</font></td></table></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3F3F25><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/ubinnenminder.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Binnen Minder</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Gnome God</span><br>  Posts: 121<br> <font color=#F4CC10>(6/12/01 11:09:31 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fthecrossroadstavern8833frm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=252.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Changes to Verant Policy</span><hr size=1> Eh, anyone with a minimal idea of what Security means isn't going to be hacked.<br><br>I only give my password to people I can go beat up in RL, and my password is NOT a dictionary word or an easy number sequence (12121212, 020380 &lt;birthdate&gt;, 680231342 &lt;SSN&gt; ).  My only PW flaw is that I haven't changed it in too long.<br><br>And, of course, I'm not gullible enough to give ANY stranger my PW (required for guide app, from what I hear...even if I was inclined to apply, I wouldn't be anymore) no matter HOW official the mail sounds. <p>Binnen Minder<br>Gnome God & <br>Eternal Valor officer <br>Zebuxoruk Server</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#564E39><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/ullewyndesperado.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Llewyn Desperado</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 11<br> <font color=#F4CC10>(6/12/01 11:20:55 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fthecrossroadstavern8833frm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=252.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Changes to Verant Policy</span><hr size=1> I hate to disagree but you can be hacked even provided you take deeper security steps than what is mentioned in Verant official recommendations. <br> <p>Llewyn Desperado <BR><BR>Zebuxoruk</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3F3F25><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/ukhorosatwork.showPublicProfile?language=EN>KhorosAtWork</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_lightning.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 22<br> <font color=#F4CC10>(6/12/01 2:13:27 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fthecrossroadstavern8833frm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?t